generate() - Method in class bantam.codegenmips.MipsCodeGenerator
Generate assembly file

In particular, will need to do the following: 1 - start the data section 2 - generate data for the garbage collector 3 - generate string constants 4 - generate class name table 5 - generate object templates 6 - generate dispatch tables 7 - start the text section 8 - generate initialization subroutines 9 - generate user-defined methods See the lab manual for the details of each of these steps.
